data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!!! Motivated seller! This charming residence presents a delightful blend of style and functionality. Corner lot with a great curb appeal, wide 2-car epoxied garage, RV gate, and lovely desert landscaping welcome you. Come inside to discover a welcoming great room with a neutral palette, sliding doors to the back, recessed lighting, and wood-look tile flooring. The impressive kitchen boasts SS appliances, granite counters, ample cabinetry, and an island w/breakfast bar. Soft carpet adds comfort to the bedrooms! The primary bedroom has an ensuite with dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Let's not forget the perfectly sized backyard featuring a relaxing covered patio! With your creative ideas, you can make it an ideal outdoor oasis. Don't miss this gem!
